text: Salta is a city in the north of Argentina. It is the capital of Salta Province. In 2010, 618,375 people lived there. file:Salta-Square2.jpg file:Salta-Street1.jpg file:Catedral_de_Salta_1.jpg Category:Cities in Argentina Category:Capitals of Argentine provinces Category:Salta Province
